<span id="freeTextContainer12940754668577812836">I was searching through highly rated books Amazon to find something to read and found this one. It shouldn&apos;t be highly rated. It follows a questionable plot line, and deals with subject matter that makes you wince. The mystery crime syndicate is a run of the mill organization that commits heinous crimes anonymously and is too mysterious for the author to explain. The characters are plastic and their actions are not believable. The ending of the book was quite ridiculous. That might make it sound</span>
  <span id="freeText12940754668577812836" style="display:none">I was searching through highly rated books Amazon to find something to read and found this one. It shouldn't be highly rated. It follows a questionable plot line, and deals with subject matter that makes you wince. The mystery crime syndicate is a run of the mill organization that commits heinous crimes anonymously and is too mysterious for the author to explain. The characters are plastic and their actions are not believable. The ending of the book was quite ridiculous. That might make it sound interesting, it's not, it's just bad. Please don't read it.</span>
